In a [[supersymmetry|supersymmetric]] [[quantum field theory]], a '''superghost''' is a [[fermionic field|fermionic]] [[Faddeev–Popov ghost]], which is used in the [[gauge fixing]] of a [[fermion]]ic [[symmetry]] [[Generating set of a group|generator]].

